chronic health condition, and often these chronic health conditions can be

480
00:27:50.450 --> 00:27:53.970
debilitating, life-threatening, and actually lifelong.

481
00:27:54.010 --> 00:27:57.870
And so it really begs for us to step back and think whether

482
00:27:57.890 --> 00:28:01.260
that metric of five-year overall survival is the appropriate

483
00:28:01.290 --> 00:28:04.390
metric to use because it really questions the

484
00:28:04.470 --> 00:28:06.330
quality of that cure.

485
00:28:07.760 --> 00:28:10.930
The other challenge, and I think what's important to recognize about these chronic

486
00:28:10.950 --> 00:28:14.630
health care conditions, is that there is a variation in the

487
00:28:14.710 --> 00:28:18.340
