00:28:32.410 --> 00:28:36.040
see a lot of pediatric patients will have presentation and

493
00:28:36.070 --> 00:28:39.230
manifestations of their endocrinopathies as early as within the first

494
00:28:40.330 --> 00:28:44.050
few years of the cancer diagnosis, but that's really not the end.

