497
00:28:50.430 --> 00:28:54.190
So I think that that really is another reason why survivorship care is important,

498
00:28:54.230 --> 00:28:58.010
because it crosses that arc lifespan from pediatric to adulthood,

499
00:28:58.370 --> 00:29:01.719
and it further highlights the importance of transition and the

500
00:29:02.070 --> 00:29:06.030
knowledge base that we have to bring to our survivors once they transition

501
00:29:06.070 --> 00:29:06.950
to adult care.

502
00:29:08.370 --> 00:29:11.610
So I adopted this slide from Dr. Les Robison and Smita Bhadia.

503
00:29:11.690 --> 00:29:15.630
So Les Robison recently retired. He was an epidemiologist who I think has

