00:29:15.650 --> 00:29:16.930
done tremendous

505
00:29:18.890 --> 00:29:22.410
research in the field of pediatric cancer survivorship.

506
00:29:22.970 --> 00:29:26.860
And what really this slide shows is a paradigm of research that we have

507
00:29:26.990 --> 00:29:30.770
used in survivorship. And if you focus on the right

508
00:29:30.850 --> 00:29:34.810
side aspect of this slide, what we've really done in the past few decades is

509
00:29:34.870 --> 00:29:38.719
to harness epidemiology and biostatistics to really through

510
00:29:38.770 --> 00:29:42.460
observational studies, establish that risk association between

511
00:29:42.490 --> 00:29:46.440
