00:30:13.790 --> 00:30:15.950
affect health-related quality of life.

521
00:30:16.370 --> 00:30:20.350
But we're reaching, to me, a time point where we need to really bring

522
00:30:20.430 --> 00:30:24.090
all this data together and start incorporating that into

523
00:30:24.130 --> 00:30:27.350
mechanistic studies to really ask the why and the

524
00:30:27.510 --> 00:30:31.480
how of the survivorship, the biology of survivorship, and I think that this is

