00:30:31.530 --> 00:30:35.290
where we really have room to make difference in terms of how we approach research,

526
00:30:35.650 --> 00:30:39.610
and ultimately for those to lead to implementation of clinical trials

527
00:30:39.670 --> 00:30:43.590
where we can use that mechanistic knowledge, to essentially have

528
00:30:43.650 --> 00:30:47.558
either preventionOf these late effects after the exposure has

