00:32:06.618 --> 00:32:08.898
And finally, I would like to

554
00:32:10.038 --> 00:32:13.738
offer a new model of what I call redefining survivorship from 2.0 to

555
00:32:13.758 --> 00:32:14.358
3.0.

556
00:32:15.558 --> 00:32:18.938
So I think to start this, we really need to step back and

557
00:32:18.978 --> 00:32:22.618
