00:35:11.318 --> 00:35:14.338
that multi-mechanistic phenotype that we just discussed.

609
00:35:15.298 --> 00:35:18.608
So the CBR3 gene is actually on chromosome 21.

610
00:35:18.678 --> 00:35:22.658
It's expressed in the heart. It's more prevalent in Black individuals, and the

611
00:35:22.698 --> 00:35:26.298
CBR3 gene is actually important for metabolism of

612
00:35:26.338 --> 00:35:30.058
doxorubicin, particularly to the

613
00:35:30.118 --> 00:35:33.898
toxic alcohol derivative is what actually causes toxicity to

