00:37:08.618 --> 00:37:12.418
host and the environment, which is the treatment that you

642
00:37:12.478 --> 00:37:16.348
give as part of the cancer that can kind of predispose to the dreaded outcome of

643
00:37:16.398 --> 00:37:18.978
cardiomyopathy that can have significant

