01:10:57.642 --> 01:11:01.162
which was this prepubescent breast cancer. They cut it out.

1215
01:11:01.202 --> 01:11:04.142
Unfortunately, it came back. They cut it out again. It came back again.

1216
01:11:04.182 --> 01:11:06.262
