01:13:58.398 --> 01:14:01.418
So we're really interested in that question as our cohort gets

1268
01:14:01.458 --> 01:14:05.168
bigger with RNA sequencing. I think the social media

1269
01:14:05.238 --> 01:14:09.138
outreach efforts are underutilized, especially for patients

1270
01:14:09.178 --> 01:14:12.818
with rare cancers. And to me, germline testing should be universal, not

1271
01:14:12.858 --> 01:14:13.478
